Step to Deploy Simple Web App (without Cloud Data Store) in GCP
==============================================================================

Step 1: Get new credentials on Gcloud Command line

gcloud auth application-default login

Step 2: cd into the cloudybasket-hello-world-src folder

cd cloudybasket-hello-world-src

Step 3: Deploy and test on a local environment

sudo pip install -r requirements.txt

Step 4: Run local development server

dev_appserver.py app.yaml

Step 5: Deploy to App Engine

gcloud app deploy --version cloudybasket-hello-world

Step 6: View the app deployment information

gcloud app describe

Step 6: Open the app in a browser

gcloud app browse
